     <body>
     <div type="poem">
   <pb facs="5"/>
   <head>To his Friend M<seg rend="sup">r</seg>
      <hi>Patrick Hannay.</hi>
   </head>
   <lg>
      <l>FRiend I am glad that you haue brought to light,</l>
      <l>A Husband fit for <hi>Ouerburies</hi> Wife;</l>
      <l>Whose chastity might else suspected be,</l>
      <l>Wanting too long a Husbands company:</l>
      <l>But now being match'd so well by your endeauour,</l>
      <l>Shee'll liue a chast <hi>Penelope</hi> for euer.</l>
      <l>And you braue <hi>Ouerbury</hi> make to be,</l>
      <l>Your brother in law by act of ingeny.</l>
   </lg>
   <p>
      <hi>W. Iewell.</hi>
   </p>
</div>
